== Usage ==

This template creates an [[WP:EL|external link]] to a [[Google 翻译|Google Translate]] page, which can translate the text from a [[網頁|Web page]] in a source language to a destination language. Syntax:

 <nowiki>{{Google translation|</nowiki>''destination language code''|''source language code''|''URL of page to translate''|''link text''<nowiki>}}</nowiki>

If you leave the <code>''link text''</code> argument blank, “Google translation” appears as the default text.

Some URLs that contain special characters, such as <code>&</code> or <code>=</code>, will break the template. The solution is to prepend the URL with <code>3=</code>, for example <code><nowiki>{{Google translation|ru|en|3=http://www.example.org/this-url-contains-=}}</nowiki></code> resulting in {{Google translation|ru|en|3=http://www.example.org/this-url-contains-=}}

